m/uploads/default/original/2X/f/f76d17976d6b2c69167c10a1a18ad57e365c59be.png","https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/40b20273217e1b18c59bbcd3f48b6ecca758706c.png","https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/e/ed778e8997d71cec69276a0a32dbb603eb48ffc9.png","https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/45a3d4a0cf7fba317fc285700037318d60dfa27d.png","https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0f1453d113f15d43bcedff19610229a7f75ebf60.png","https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/6708d8959440b8805afc8470858dfedc048bcaa7.png","https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5a0098f13086eababf4f3999ed7201d14098ef6a.jpeg"]},"payload":{"url":"","schema":"20231218A","file":"content.txt","text":"Image: https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/185aba8e47a1d73575862869f8dd0c602eebe6b3.png]\nDescription: The image displays a terminal window featuring a Git command session. The user, identified as \u0022victor@HP-book-Viktor,\u0022 is working within the directory \u0022c/OrigamProjects/MyApplication\u0022 on the master branch. The commands executed include \u0022git add .,\u0022 followed by \u0022git commit -m \u0027Version with added entities\u0027.\u0022 The output indicates that two files were changed during this commit, documenting 40,570 insertions and 40,673 deletions. A new file was created, noted as \u0022model/myapplication/DataEntity/myapplication/Priority.orinam.\u0022 The session concludes with a command prompt, indicating readiness for additional input.\n\n\n  \n \n \n \nTortoiseGit \n In TortoiseGit, simply use the  Commit  option in the appropriate directory, and enter your message in the window: \n  \n\n\n[Image: https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/f/f76d17976d6b2c69167c10a1a18ad57e365c59be.png]\nDescription: The image depicts a TortoiseGit commit interface displayed on a Windows system, with the directory path shown as \u0022C:\\OrigamProjects\\MyApplication.\u0022 The user is committed to the \u0022master\u0022 branch and has entered the commit message \u0022Version with added entities.\u0022 Options available include \u0022Amend Last Commit,\u0022 \u0022Show diff to last commit,\u0022 and author settings indicating \u0022Viktor \u003Cviktor.ter@advantages.cz\u003E.\u0022 The changes made section lists two files: \u0022model/index.bin\u0022 with extension \u0022.bin\u0022 (status: Modified) and \u0022model/myapplication/DataEntity/myapplication/Priority.origram\u0022 with extension \u0022.origram\u0022 (status: Added). Two files are selected for the commit, and buttons for \u0022Commit,\u0022 \u0022Cancel,\u0022 and \u0022Help\u0022 are visible.\n\n\n  \n \n   Viewing saved versions \n If you need information about which versions of your application have been saved, you can list them. Your notes for each version will be helpful here. \n \n \nGit Bash \n In Git Bash, use this command: \n  git log\n  \n  \n\n\n[Image: https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/40b20273217e1b18c59bbcd3f48b6ecca758706c.png]\nDescription: The image displays a terminal interface showing the output of the command \u0022git log\u0022 executed in a Git project directory at the path \u0022/c/OrigamProjects/MyApplication.\u0022 It includes a list of commit history detailing two commits. The first commit has the hash \u002270f39625a31c37f12441ac3ca20418979dcb8e15,\u0022 authored by \u0022Vktor \u003Cviktor.ter@advantages.cz\u003E\u0022 on \u0022Thu Jan 16 14:23:09 2025 \u002B0100,\u0022 with the message \u0022Version with added entities.\u0022 The second commit features the hash \u00221bb3684a202aef949143eb0b7fe2419c3c4f027a,\u0022 authored by the same individual on \u0022Thu Jan 16 13:20:40 2025 \u002B0100,\u0022 labeled as \u0022Initial commit.\u0022 The terminal prompt indicates the current branch is \u0022master,\u0022 with \u0022HEAD\u0022 pointing to the latest commit.\n\n\n  \n \n \n \nTortoiseGit \n In TortoiseGit, use the  Show log  option, and you will see a log like this: \n  \n\n\n[Image: https://community.origam.com/uploads/default/original/2X/e/ed778e8997d71cec69276a0a32dbb603eb48ffc9.png]\nDescription: The image displays the TortoiseGit log messages interface for a project titled \u0022MyApplication,\u0022 located at the path \u0022C:\\OrigamProjects\\\u0022. The log messages are filtered between the dates 1/16/2025 to 1/16/2025 and show two entries: \u0022master Version with added entities\u0022 authored by Viktor and \u0022Initial commit\u0022 also by Viktor. Below, details include SHA-1 hash \u00227f039625a31c37f12441ac3a20418979dcb8e15,\u0022 and stats indicating the \u0022model/index.bin\u0022 and \u0022model/myapplication/DataEntity/myapplication/Priority.origram\u0022 files, noting the former as modified with 40,728 lines added and 40,673 lines removed. The interface features options for refreshing, statistics, and walking behavior, and shows the selection of two revisions with line numbers reflecting changes made.\n\n\n","vector_provider":"AI.Ollama.OllamaTextEmbeddingGenerator","vector_generator":"__","last_update":"2026-05-01T23:39:11"},"vector":[-0.020200118,-0.0239023,-0.041963723,0.03702878,-0.006238945,-0.037289992,-0.0099032,-0.024356138,-0.0112366155,0.014874844,0.010896647,-0.010632732,-0.02296501,0.016544357,0.0074817957,-0.0064632767,-0.029798755,0.018566223,0.0139102535,0.020490233,0.000121778954,-0.013643091,0.065683454,0.022024134,-0.020044416,0.014970776,0.008268244,-0.03704324,0.028890502,0.023619654,0.03235531,-0.013872854,0.010506133,-0.032567143,-0.03540505,0.045303207,0.030221526,-0.016006356,-0.023618853,0.002406928,0.017070718,-0.020988176,-0.0056853504,-0.0011854859,-0.020735847,-0.010108716,-0.0046869977,0.0021157037,-0.009789281,-0.019246737,-0.0087384805,-0.016186384,0.014222058,-0.0375557,0.020022145,0.07103722,-0.04962343,-0.026552774,-0.06104277,0.007689763,-0.014402318,0.044047147,-0.01754189,-0.058302652,-0.0303096